node.text:
Happy Mother’s Day!(10/5)
Celebrating this day at home during Circuit Breaker....unconventional way!
We ordered a variety of Mexican food from  @vatossg, chicken wings, fried mushrooms, guacamole dip, fries n nuggets, kueh lapis and bubble teas.
Enjoy and have a great evening everyone!😃😋
.

#happymothersday❤️ #vatossg #circuitbreakersg #stayhomestaysafe #covid_19 #socialdistancing2020 #ahpekeats
